WEBVTT

00:02:59.349 --> 00:03:01.959
which feeds, nurtures and supports us,

00:03:01.959 --> 00:03:06.337
and brings the used blood back
to be renewed.

00:03:06.337 --> 00:03:10.659
In the Amazon, things happen similarly.

00:03:10.659 --> 00:03:15.766
We'll start by talking about
the power of all these processes.

00:03:15.766 --> 00:03:20.387
This is an image

00:03:20.387 --> 00:03:23.198
of rain in motion.

00:03:23.198 --> 00:03:27.211
What you see there
is the years passing in seconds.

00:03:27.211 --> 00:03:30.159
Rains all over the world.
What do you see?